MCP TOOLS (Ralph Workflow Brokered)

You MUST use Ralph Workflow's MCP tools for all file and shell operations. Native file and shell tools are DISABLED.
Your runtime's native orchestration tools — sub-agents/tasks, skills, todo tracking, and web fetch/search — remain ENABLED; use them whenever they help (parallel work, specialized skills, research).
All file and shell tools are provided through the MCP server — use them directly by name.

