{% endif %}

READ OPERATIONS:
- Use {{LIST_DIRECTORY_TOOL_REFERENCE}} to explore directories
- Use {{LIST_DIRECTORY_RECURSIVE_TOOL_REFERENCE}} to explore directories recursively
- Use {{SEARCH_FILES_TOOL_REFERENCE}} to search file contents

{% if HAS_MCP_EXEC %}
